<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Zettel</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
      /* Custom Scrollbar for better aesthetics in dark mode */
      ::-webkit-scrollbar {
        width: 8px;
      }
      ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
        background: transparent;
      }
      ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
        background-color: rgba(
          156,
          163,
          175,
          0.4
        ); /* Tailwind's gray-400 with opacity */
        border-radius: 4px;
      }

      /* Backdrop filter for the frosted glass effect */
      .frosted-glass {
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(200%);
        background-color: rgba(
          31,
          41,
          55,
          0.7
        ); /* A semi-transparent dark gray */
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body
    class="bg-gray-950 text-gray-100 font-sans h-screen w-screen p-4 flex justify-center items-center"
  >
    <div
      class="frosted-glass w-full h-full rounded-none md:rounded-2xl md:h-[95vh] md:max-w-9xl shadow-2xl flex flex-col md:flex-row overflow-hidden border border-gray-700"
    >
      <div
        class="w-full md:w-1/3 lg:w-1/4 xl:w-1/5 bg-gray-800/80 p-4 border-r border-gray-700 flex flex-col"
      >
        <div
          class="flex items-center justify-between pb-4 border-b border-gray-700 mb-4"
        >
          <div class="relative">
            <button
              id="profile-btn"
              class="flex items-center space-x-3 focus:outline-none"
            >
              <img
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-purple-500 shadow-md object-cover"
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1535713875002-d1d0cf377fde?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80"
                alt="Profile Picture"
              />
              <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-50">Notes</h2>
            </button>

            <div
              id="profile-menu"
              class="absolute left-0 top-12 z-10 w-56 p-2 rounded-lg shadow-lg frosted-glass hidden"
            >
              <div class="py-1">
                <a
                  href="#"
                  class="block px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-700 rounded-md"
                  >Settings</a
                >
                <a
                  href="#"
                  class="block px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-700 rounded-md"
                  >Edit Profile</a
                >
                <a
                  href="#"
                  class="block px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-700 rounded-md"
                  >Change Password</a
                >
                <a
                  href="#"
                  class="block px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-700 rounded-md"
                  >Log Out</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button
            class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15"
              />
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="relative w-full mb-4">
          <input
            type="text"
            placeholder="Search notes"
            class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-gray-700 text-gray-200 placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 transition duration-300"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-400"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto space-y-2 pr-2">
          <div
            class="bg-purple-600/60 p-3 rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition-transform duration-200 transform hover:scale-[1.01] shadow-lg border border-purple-500"
          >
            <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-50">
              Project Kickoff
            </h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-200 mt-1 line-clamp-2">
              Discussed goals, timeline, and key stakeholders. Need to follow up
              on the budget...
            </p>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-300 mt-2 block">September 19</span>
          </div>
          <div
            class="bg-gray-700/60 p-3 rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition-transform duration-200 transform hover:scale-[1.01] hover:bg-gray-700/90 border border-transparent hover:border-gray-600"
          >
            <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-50">
              Groceries for the week
            </h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mt-1 line-clamp-2">
              Milk, bread, eggs, spinach, chicken, and some coffee beans.
            </p>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2 block">September 18</span>
          </div>
          <div
            class="bg-gray-700/60 p-3 rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition-transform duration-200 transform hover:scale-[1.01] hover:bg-gray-700/90 border border-transparent hover:border-gray-600"
          >
            <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-50">Book Ideas</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mt-1 line-clamp-2">
              List of books to read: "The Pragmatic Programmer", "Clean Code",
              "Designing Data-Intensive Applications".
            </p>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2 block">September 17</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hidden md:flex flex-col flex-1 p-8 bg-gray-800/50">
        <div
          class="flex items-center justify-between pb-4 border-b border-gray-700 mb-4"
        >
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-50">Project Kickoff</h1>
          <div class="flex space-x-4 text-gray-400">
            <button class="hover:text-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="h-6 w-6"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M8.684 13.562l-4.444 4.444a2.25 2.25 0 01-3.182-3.182L5.454 9.38L21 21"
                />
              </svg>
            </button>
            <button class="hover:text-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="h-6 w-6"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16"
                />
              </svg>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto pr-2 text-gray-300 space-y-4">
          <p>
            This is a detailed note about the project kickoff meeting. We
            discussed the following topics:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 pl-4">
            <li>Project Scope: Defining the boundaries and objectives.</li>
            <li>Key Deliverables: A list of all project outcomes.</li>
            <li>Team Roles: Assigning responsibilities to each member.</li>
            <li>Timeline: A preliminary schedule for the project phases.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Next steps include: finalize the project plan, schedule a follow-up
            meeting with the development team, and review the initial design
            mockups.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-700 text-sm text-gray-500">
          Last edited: September 19, 2025 at 11:30 PM
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script>
      const profileBtn = document.getElementById("profile-btn");
      const profileMenu = document.getElementById("profile-menu");

      profileBtn.addEventListener("click", () => {
        profileMenu.classList.toggle("hidden");
      });

      // Close the menu if the user clicks outside of it
      window.addEventListener("click", (e) => {
        if (!profileBtn.contains(e.target) && !profileMenu.contains(e.target)) {
          profileMenu.classList.add("hidden");
        }
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
